{"word":"γαῦρος","slug":"γαῦρος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>γαῦρος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:γαίω'><el>γαίω</el></a>\n<p/><i>exulting in</i> a thing, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>: <a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>haughty, disdainful</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>; of a calf, <i>skittish</i>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b>:— <el>τὸ γ.  γαυρότης</el>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/>"}]}